rows.label: qst502014_msg0001
rows.name: Um... What happened?

rows.label: qst502014_msg0002
rows.name:
Sulala is a guide, mo. She was supposed
to show the newly arrived Ukiukii around
the Liberalitas Archipelago, mo.

rows.label: qst502014_msg0003
rows.name:
But... she got more excited
than Ukiukii, fell, and
hit her head, mo...

rows.label: qst502014_msg0005
rows.name:
I understand... I'll get
a doctor right away...

rows.label: qst502014_msg0006
rows.name:
Please wait, mo! It's too
late, mo! Her heart has
already stopped beating, mo!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0007
rows.name:
Please use your lightning power
to shock her back to life, mo!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0008
rows.name: What!?

rows.label: qst502014_msg0009
rows.name:
There's no time to hesitate, mo!
It's a race against time, mo!!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0010
rows.name: Ugh... I'll give it a try!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0011
rows.name: Momo!!!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0012
rows.name: A great success, mo!!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0013
rows.name:
I got so excited, I felt like I
was ascending to heaven, mo...

rows.label: qst502014_msg0014
rows.name:
Now, let's get serious and
start the tour of the
Liberalitas Archipelago, mo!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0015
rows.name: Wait a moment, mo!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0016
rows.name: You should thank this person first, mo.

rows.label: qst502014_msg0017
rows.name: Should I, mo?

rows.label: qst502014_msg0018
rows.name:
I don't really understand,
but thank you very much, mo.

rows.label: qst502014_msg0019
rows.name: N-no... I'm glad I could help.

rows.label: qst502014_msg0020
rows.name:
You saved Sulala's life,
mo! Thank you, mo!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0021
rows.name: It seems my power isn't enough...

rows.label: qst502014_msg0022
rows.name: I'm sorry...
